Class IntArrayWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • infodynamics.utils.IntArrayWrapper

  • public class IntArrayWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    IntArrayWrapper is used to wrap a long array so as to be able to give it a hash value for placement into a hash table.
